&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Work collaboratively with all team members on various aspects of project execution, ensuring clear communication, alignment, and efficiency throughout all project stages&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
